<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 8. Type localities of Coelotes septus Wang et al., 1990, Draconarius lingdang sp. nov., D. substrophadatus sp. nov., Orumcekia cipingensis sp. nov., and Tonsilla shuikouensis sp. nov." , "Figure 4. Draconarius lingdang sp. nov., female paratype A habitus, dorsal view B same, ventral view C epigyne, ventral view D vulva, dorsal view. Scale bars: 1 mm (A, B); 0.1 mm (C, D). Abbreviations: At - atrium, CD - copulatory duct, CO - copulatory opening, ET - epigynal teeth, FD - fertilization duct, Spe - spermatheca." , "Figure 3. Draconarius lingdang sp. nov., male holotype A habitus, dorsal view B same, ventral view C palp, prolateral view D same, ventral view E same, retrolateral view. Scale bars: 1 mm (A, B); 0.1 mm (C-E). Abbreviations: CF - cymbial furrow, Con - conductor, DAC - dorsal apophysis of conductor, Em - embolus, MA - median apophysis, RTA - retrolateral tibial apophysis, VTA - ventrolateral tibial apophysis." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529555" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529551" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/529550" .

